    "body":  "Enhance the dashboard by integrating an AI-generated insights section into the existing “Recent Activity” panel. This will demonstrate the potential of predictive intelligence within the IMQ platform and offer users helpful, proactive system guidance.\n\n**Requirements**\n\n**Panel Update**\n\n- Rename Panel Title:\n\nRecent Activity → System Updates (AI + Activity)\n\n**Panel Layout (Visual)**\n🧠 Recommended Actions (AI)\n- 3 workers lack current job assignments\n- 2 assessments flagged for override review\n- 1 cert expiring in next 7 days (Mike J.)\n\n─────────────────────────────\n\n🕒 Recent Activity\n- Jane Doe assessed for Quality Specialist – Qualified\n- Override approved for Mike Johnson – QA Lead\n- New CV uploaded and parsed successfully\n\n**Labeling**\n\n- Add a subtle label to the AI section:\n\n🧠 AI-Generated | Last Updated: [timestamp]\n\n**Behavior**\n\n- Static (for now): Use placeholder recommendations.\n- Optional: Include a “🔄 Refresh Suggestions” button (non-functional, placeholder).\n- Optional: Add a hover tooltip on the “🧠 AI-Generated” label:\n\n     _These recommendations are based on recent user activity and qualification data._\n\n**Implementation Notes**\n\n- No new route/page required.\n- Do not redirect on click; this is a display-only feature for POC.\n- Keep structure lightweight and consistent with the visual theme.\n- Consider using simple conditional logic for the demo (e.g., if a worker lacks assignment, show related suggestion).",
